{"tid":1942913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際突發] 威爾斯親王查理斯確診武漢病毒","createTime":"2020-03-25T10:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T11:06:34.000Z","uid":152636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9c66b4efc9c958021b875b6b986c0d6fcf214ccc","tid":1942913,"uid":152636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:44:12.000Z","msg":"Prince Charles has tested positive for coronavirus, it has been confirmed.<br />\n<br />\nThe 71-year-old is heir to the throne.<br />\n<br />\nHis mother, the Queen, has already left London to be at Windsor Castle.<br />\n<br />\nPrince of Wales&rsquo; office says: &ldquo;He has been displaying mild symptoms but otherwise remains in good health and has been working from home throughout the last few days as usual.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nHis wife, Camilla has been tested but she does not have the virus.<br />\n<br />\nBoth Prince Charles and Camilla are self isolating. They are currently at their home Burnham on the Balmoral Estate in Scotland, according to ITV reporter Chris Ship.<br />\n<br />\nPrince Charles&rsquo;s office says: &ldquo;It is not possible to ascertain from whom the Prince caught the virus owing to the high number of engagements he carried out in his public role during recent weeks.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/prince-wales-charles-coronavirus-covid19-17976203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walesonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fwales-news%2Fprince-wales-charles-coronavirus-covid19-17976203&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=cb8dfdfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/prince-wales-charles-coronavirus-covid19-17976203</a>"},{"pid":"e72cf463b42320ea83edde779b8664ffb7851b3b","tid":1942913,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9